Germany Prepared to Increase Commerzbank Stake, Spiegel Says

-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 
2011-12-04T14:03:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-04/germany-prepared-to-increase-commerzbank-stake-spiegel-says.html
Germany ’s government is ready to
increase its stake in  Commerzbank AG  should the nation’s second-
biggest lender fail to raise the capital stipulated by new
requirements by next summer, Spiegel  reported , citing
unidentified government officials.  A further investment from the government would probably
mean nationalization of the bank, Spiegel said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
